### Countries API Tests

#Local environment URL
@base_url = http://localhost:8000

#Staging URL
# @base_url = https://staging.viraltogether.com
#Production URL
# @base_url = https://api.viraltogether.com


### Get All Countries
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries

### Search Countries by Name
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries?search=united

### Search Countries by Code
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries?search=US

### Filter Countries by Region
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries?region=Europe

### Get Countries with Pagination
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries?limit=10&offset=0

### Get All Available Regions
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries/regions

### Get Specific Country by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries/1

### Get Country with Search and Region Filter
GET {{base_url}}/api/countries?search=united&region=North America&limit=20 